Unsurprisingly, Graham=E2=80=99s name has come up a lot in recent days. =E2=
=80=9CNow we know
that Bezos is no Katharine Graham,=E2=80=9D Marty Baron, the storied editor=
 who led the Post through its =E2=80=9CDemocracy Dies in Darkness=E2=80=9D =
phase, wrote ( https://www.theatlantic.com/ideas/archive/2025/03/bezos-appe=
ase-trump-administration/681899/?utm_source=3Dcopy-link&utm_medium=3Dsocial=
