email_action&utm_source=3Dcustomer.io&utm_term=3Df6c60617da42abd12a ) this =
week in The Atlantic. =E2=80=9CIt has been sad and unnerving to watch Bezos=
 fall so terribly short of her standard
as he confronts the return of Donald Trump to the White House. It=E2=80=99s=
